''Lazes, Ma.
- Evo pisma''

8
00:03:56,903 --> 00:03:59,167
Pokazi mi pismo

9
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:04,606
Shubhankar! Moj Devdas dolazi!
- Stvarno?

10
00:04:04,978 --> 00:04:07,139
Prenesi dobre vesti svom bratu

11
